     <div class="mainleftcon"> 
      <div class="mainleft_title"> 
       <h1> “人神共定”的规则是“人神共守”的底线 </h1> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_two"> 
       <div class="mainleft_from">
         作者：
        <a href="http://toutiao.weiyoubaba.com/m30968/">倪卫涛</a>&nbsp;&nbsp; 发布时间：2017-02-02
       </div> 
      </div> 
      <div class="mainleft_three"> 
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">老虎袭人是老虎的本性使然，参观者逃票是破坏“人神共定”的规则，该同情的是那头智商没有人类高明的老虎。人之所以比老虎高贵，是因为进化比动物高级，然而人类破坏了大家本应共同遵守的规则，也只有自食其果。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-ratio="0.55625" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Tda9DTzGiaNjuscl32TnM9C2PRpWDj0qtwuSPFToDSgqr8rg87uEuOUwEBa54RGABdXDjukBiaNpJ8yyaqHkB38w/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" height="389" style="margin: 1em auto; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; display: block; border-radius: 4px;" width="699" /></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word;">“人神共定”的规则</span></strong></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">无论任何人还是动物，规则面前，万生平等。所谓的高贵和低贱不过是自以为是者歧视和奴役的托词和借口，即使是人类作为一个将要入园游玩的普通人，你的规则就是遵守园规，进园买票是你的基本原则，触碰底线就是失败者的开端，逃票翻墙本身是一种违规行为，聪明的人绝不会虎口送食，想要通过万般的侥幸占得一时的便宜都是一种愚蠢，自食其果是悲剧者的结局。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word;">悲剧者的借口</span></strong></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">为了节省130元铤而走险，在许多人看来，雅戈尔动物园的门票比起北京动物园的门票15元足足高出了八倍之多，责任在于动物园的高门票之故，反而同情起了那位逃票者，悲剧者总有自己的借口，岂不知这是失败者的托词。作为一个公民，连遵守最基本的规则都做不到，岂不是一种失败，却把失败当做需要同情的资本，更是可悲的，在法律和规则面前，容不得任何人蔑视和破坏大家都共同遵守的规则。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-ratio="0.603125" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Tda9DTzGiaNjuscl32TnM9C2PRpWDj0qtqsHr3pdYDtaxcIf7eonyYbbJtVbfGLoFU6Eo3OAmqzQbTuqvI0GBwQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="640" height="422" style="margin: 1em auto; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; display: block; border-radius: 4px;" width="700" /></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong><span style="border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word;">被冤的老虎</span></strong></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">自然规律和自然选择是生物的共同准则，纵使残酷和冷血，但老虎就是食肉动物，而且在已经濒临灭绝的时代，圈养在动物园的老虎已经消失了野性，雅戈尔动物园为了培养老虎的野性，专门训练了老虎的野性，让已经被驯化的老虎显露自己凶猛的本性，以此吸引更多的游客，但在老虎本性爆发的那一刹那却被击毙，遗憾的是并未成功救下这位逃票者。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img data-ratio="1.0545454545454545" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Tda9DTzGiaNjuscl32TnM9C2PRpWDj0qtdZbITFplicXK30EMESPyyNQfTR4ia7GJvhBevpbMY6UicSpzANdf8lwGw/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-type="jpeg" data-w="440" height="464" style="margin: 1em auto; border: 0px; font-style: inherit; font-variant: inherit; font-weight: inherit; font-stretch: inherit; font-size: inherit; line-height: inherit; font-family: inherit; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; display: block; border-radius: 4px;" width="440" /></p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">生命面前，万生平等，太过聪明的人类，切勿贪得一时的便宜，玩得一手小聪明，去赌上生命，因小失大，虽然老虎的智商有限，但却不会丧失最基本的觅食能力。</p>
       <p style="margin-top: 1em; border: 0px; font-stretch: inherit; font-size:auto; line-height: 27px; font-family: helvetica, Arial, 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', simsun; vertical-align: baseline; word-break: break-word; color: rgb(93, 93, 93); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></p>
       <hr />
       <p><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:auto; line-height: 31.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br /></span></p>
       <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:auto; line-height: 31.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">作者：倪卫涛，超级自媒体，畅销书《媒体+时代：开启未来新商业的秘密》、《互联网+风口》作者，今日头条、百度百家、搜狐科技、钛媒体等50多家科技媒体的专栏作者，淘宝、京东、苏宁、微博、</span><span data-key="购物" data-word="" data-type="0" data-typestr="" class="hot-wrap show" style="max-width: 100%; font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.1; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-size:auto; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><a class="hotword-mark" style="color: rgb(18, 183, 245); max-width: 100%; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: dotted; word-wrap: break-word !important; box-sizing: border-box !important;">购物圈</a></span><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:auto; line-height: 31.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">、今日头条等全渠道达人，微博@倪卫涛。&nbsp;</span></p>
       <p style="text-align: left;"><span style="color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:auto; line-height: 31.5px; text-align: justify; white-space: pre-wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>
       <p><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-src="http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/Tda9DTzGiaNiaVr4AGEMy2Mk3nb2ia6licQQNibmib6icUzlM4hib2GeFMEmBtHCqpITKkvUZicP207yddmiaVMcicgFc6LHQ/0?wx_fmt=jpeg" data-ratio="1.30375" data-w="800" /></p>
